A^*A
\ell_2
A^*Av=\sigma^2 v
\sigma^2=\left\Vert A^*A\right\Vert=\left\Vert A\right\Vert^2
\frac{\left\Vert A^*Av\right\Vert_1}{\left\Vert v\right\Vert_1}=\frac{\left\Vert \left\Vert A\right\Vert^2v\right\Vert_1}{\left\Vert v\right\Vert_1}=\left\Vert A\right\Vert^2.
M=\left\Vert A\right\Vert_{\infty\to \infty}
N=\left\Vert A\right\Vert_{1\to 1}
\left\vert x^*Ay\right\vert\leq\left\Vert A\right\Vert\left\Vert x\right\Vert\left\Vert y\right\Vert
\left\Vert A\right\Vert^2\leq\left\Vert A^*A\right\Vert_{1\to 1}=\max_{u,v\neq 0}\frac{\left\vert u^*A^*Av\right\vert}{\left\Vert u\right\Vert_\infty\left\Vert v\right\Vert_1}\\ \leq \max_{u,v\neq 0}\frac{\left\Vert Au\right\Vert_\infty\left\Vert Av\right\Vert_1}{\left\Vert u\right\Vert_\infty\left\Vert v\right\Vert_1}=\left\Vert A\right\Vert_{\infty\to\infty}\cdot \left\Vert A\right\Vert_{1\to 1}.
